</div><br />
<ul><li style=""><i>Reduced latency of kill notifications in Crucible</i></li><li style=""><i>Improved damage validation systems to reduce the effectiveness of players with extreme lag</i></li><li style=""><i>Improved accuracy of network quality meters slightly</i></li></ul><br />
<br /></div>
			
